# 17. Scenario: Azure Remote Backend for Terraform State

Example configuration:

```hcl
terraform {
 backend "azurerm" {
   resource_group_name  = "tfstate-rg"
   storage_account_name = "tfstate123"
   container_name       = "tfstate"
